==English==
=== Adjectival Phrase ===
'''spic and span'''
# {{idiom}} perfectly [[clean]]
#:''I mopped up the kitchen floor so it was '''spic and span'''.''
#[first coined in American Negro community in the 1950s] a mixed Puerto Rican and Negro couple (Green, p.390)

